This is markdownblog, a bloggingsoftware based on markdown and dropbox.

Here's how to get started:

- Download into empty folder in /var/www (or whereever your webserver resides)
- Run Bundler to install dependencies
- Run server --start
- Visit yourserver:4567 and login as admin (pw:admin)
- Configure your blog
- Click update
- You're ready to go
